 TION</b><br><b><u><br></u><p>In the Matter of a Board Retreat</p><p><br></p
 ><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>To:&nbsp\;Directors of the Board of Educati
 on of Independent School&nbsp\;</p><p>District No. 625</p><br><br><p>PLEASE
  TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Sectio
 n 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a Special Meeting of the Board
  of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Sc
 hools\, to be held and convened on&nbsp\;Saturday\, May 8\, 2021 beginning 
 at 8:00 a.m.&nbsp\;in Conference Rooms A and B of the Administration Buildi
 ng located at 360 Colborne Street\, at which time the Board shall conduct a
  Board Retreat.</p><br><br><b>Members of the public wishing to attend must 
 contact the Board Secretary at&nbsp\;sarah.dahlke@spps.org&nbsp\;or 612-434
 -1105 at least 24 hours in advance and must follow CDC\, Minnesota Departme
 nt of Health\, and District guidelines.&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Because all board mem
 bers will be present at 360 Colborne for the meeting\, there will be no liv
 e streaming available online\, and the public is welcome to attend in-perso
 n.&nbsp\; The meeting will be audio recorded for those who wish to listen t
 o the meeting once the recording is published.</b><br><p>May 3\, 2021</p><b
 r><p>Jeanelle Foster<br>Chair\, Board of Education</p><p>Independent School
  District No. 625&nbsp\;</p>Saint Paul Public Schools</b>
