 /p><br><br><p style="">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant
  to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a
  special meeting of the Board of Education of Independent School District N
 o. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on Tuesday\, N
 ovember 17\, 2020\, commencing at 4:30 P.M. in-person at Administration Bui
 lding\, 360 Colborne Street\, with the option of Board members participatin
 g remotely via Teams Meeting.\, at which time the Board shall move into a c
 losed session to consider strategy for labor negotiations\, including negot
 iation strategies\, developments\, discussion\, and review of labor negotia
 tion proposals for Saint Paul Supervisors' Organization\, Tri-Council\, Bus
  Drivers and Custodians as is provided for by Minnesota Statutes Section 13
 D.03. The public may monitor the open portions of the meeting via live stre
 am at <a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps.org/boe</a>.</p><br><p sty
 le="">Dated: November 12\, 2020</p><p style=""></p><br><p style="">Jeanelle
