DESCRIPTION:<br><b><p>NDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</p><p>SAINT PAUL P
 UBLIC SCHOOLS</p><br>NOTICE OF SERIES OF SPECIAL&nbsp\;</b><br><b><u>MEETIN
 GS OF THE BOARD OF EDUCATION<br></u></b><br><b><u><br></u><p>In the Matter 
 of Board Action&nbsp\;</p><p>Regarding Reopening Items</p><p><br></p><p></p
 ><p></p><p>To:&nbsp\;Directors of the Board of Education of Independent Sch
 ool&nbsp\;</p><p>District No. 625</p><br><p>PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the u
 ndersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6
 \, does hereby call a series of special meetings of the Board of Education 
 of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be 
 held and convened on:</p><br><ul><li><p>Monday\, August 31\, 2020 at 6:00 P
 .M.\;</p></li><li><p>Tuesday\, September 8\, 2020 at 4:00 P.M.\;</p></li><l
 i><p>Monday\, September 14\, 2020\;&nbsp\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, Septembe
 r 21\, 2020\;&nbsp\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, September 28\, 2020\;&nbsp\;</
 p></li><li><p>Monday\, October 5\, 2020\;&nbsp\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, Oc
 tober 12\, 2020\;&nbsp\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, October 19\, 2020\;&nbsp\;
 </p></li><li><p>and Monday\, October 26\, 2020.</p></li></ul><br><p>Each me
 eting will commence at 5:00 P.M\, unless otherwise noted\, via telephonic a
 nd video conference during which the Board will consider and act on contrac
 t items regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021\, and any other matte
 rs regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021 and/or in response to COVI
 D-19.</p><br><p>The public may monitor the open portions of the meeting via
  live stream at&nbsp\;<a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps.org/boe</a
 >.</p><br><p>August 26\, 2020</p><br><p>Jeanelle Foster<br>Chair\, Board of
  Education</p><p>Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p><p>Saint Pau
 l Public Schools</p></b>
