 <br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>To: Directors of the Board of Education of 
 Independent School District No. 625</p><p></p><p>PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that 
 the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivis
 ion 6\, does hereby call a special closed meeting of the Board of Education
  of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be
  held and convened on Tuesday\, April 23\, 2024 in Conference Room 5A of th
 e Administration Building\, located at 360 Colborne Street. The special clo
 sed meeting shall begin at 4:00 p.m.\, and the Board will discuss attorney-
