 f an appeal of a Minnesota Public Employment Relations Board decision and o
 rder\, regarding Case No. 24-U-001.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Dated: April 18\, 2
 024</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Halla Henderson</p><p>Chair\, Board of Educa
 tion Independent School District No. 625 </p><p>Saint Paul Public Schools</
 p>
