DESCRIPTION:<b><br><p>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</p><p>SAINT PAUL 
 PUBLIC SCHOOLS</p><br></b>NOTICE OF SPECIAL MEETING<br>OF THE BOARD OF EDUC
 ATION<br><br><p style="">In the Matter of a Closed Labor</p><p style="">Neg
 otiation Meeting</p><p style="font-weight: bold\;"></p><br><br><p style="fo
 nt-weight: bold\;">To:Directors of the Board of Education of Independent Sc
 hool&nbsp\;</p><p style="font-weight: bold\;">District No. 625</p><br><br><
 p style="font-weight: bold\;">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, p
 ursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby
  call a special meeting of the Board of Education of Independent School Dis
 trict No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on Wedn
 esday\, June 17\, 2020\, commencing at 3:30 P.M. via telephonic and video c
 onference\, at which time the Board shall move into a closed session to con
 sider strategy for labor negotiations\, including negotiation strategies\, 
 developments\, discussion\, and review of labor negotiation proposals for t
 he Saint Paul Principals’ Association\, AFSCME\, Professional Employees Ass
 ociation\, Bus Drivers\, Tri-Council\, and Superintendency as is provided f
 or by Minnesota Statutes Section 13D.03. The public may monitor the open po
 rtions of the meeting via live stream at <a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">
 www.spps.org/boe</a>.</p><br><p style="font-weight: bold\;">Dated: June 12\
 , 2020</p><p style="font-weight: bold\;"></p><p style="font-weight: bold\;"
 >Jeanelle Foster<br>Vice Chair\, Board of Education</p><p style="font-weigh
 t: bold\;">Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p><p style="font-wei
 ght: bold\;">Saint Paul Public Schools</p>
