UID:12f4mm44qr0o1jhkcs9r4rq41c@google.com
CREATED:20240222T212444Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</b></p><p><b>SAINT PA
 UL PUBLIC SCHOOLS</b></p><p><br></p><br><u>SPECIAL NOTICE FROM THE BOARD OF
  EDUCATION</u><br><p>In the Matter of a Series of Closed Meetings Regarding
  Labor Negotiations</p><p><u>______________________________________________
 ______________________________</u></p><br><p>To: Directors of the Board of 
 Education of Independent School </p><p>District No. 625</p><br><br><p>PLEAS
 E TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Secti
 on 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a series of special meetings 
 of the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Pa
 ul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on:</p><ul><li><p><b>Monday\, F
 ebruary 26\, 2024</b></p></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, March 4\, 2024</b></p><
 /b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, March 11\, 2024</b></p></b></li><li><b><p><b>
 Monday\, March 18\, 2024</b></p></b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, March 25\, 2
 024</b></p></b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, April 1\, 2024</b></p></b></li><l
 i><b><p><b>Monday\, April 8\, 2024</b></p></b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, Ap
 ril 15\, 2024</b></p></b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, April 22\, 2024</b></p>
 </b></li><li><b><p><b>Monday\, April 29\, 2024</b></p></b></li></ul><br><p>
 <b>Meetings will begin at 4:00 p.m. in Conference Room 5A of the Administra
 tion Building located at 360 Colborne Street</b>\, during which by majority
  public vote the Board shall move into a closed session to consider strateg
 y for labor negotiations\, including negotiation strategies\, developments\
 , discussion\, and review of labor negotiation proposals for these bargaini
 ng units including ASAP\, Educational Assistants\, Principals\, School and 
 Community Service Professionals\, Teachers\, MMSA\, PEA\, AFSCME\, Bus Driv
 ers\, CCEA\, Custodians\, Tri-Council\, Electricians\, Glaziers\, Pipe fitt
 ers\, Plumbers\, Sheet Metal Workers\, and Tri-Council Temps.\, as is provi
 ded for by Minnesota Statutes Section 13D.03</p><br><p>Following the closed
  session\, the Board shall continue in open session and\, if necessary\, sh
 all discuss and take action with respect to labor negotiations.</p><br><p>F
 ebruary 22\, 2024</p><p>Halla Henderson<br>Chair\, Board of Education</p><p
 >Independent School District No. 625 </p><br>Saint Paul Public Schools
LAST-MODIFIED:20240306T220414Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special (Closed) Meeting re: Labor Negotiations
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
