 <br><p dir="ltr">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Mi
 nnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a speci
 al meeting of the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625
 \, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on <b>Tuesday\, July
  18\, 2023 beginning immediately following the adjournment of the Regular M
 eeting of the Board of Education\, which is scheduled to begin at 5:30 p.m.
   The special meeting will convene in Conference Room 5A of the Administrat
 ion Building located at 360 Colborne Street</b>\, during which by majority 
