 ri-Council\, Bricklayers\, Carpenters\, Cement Masons\, Electricians\, Glaz
 iers\, Painters\, Pipe fitters\, Plasterers\, Plumbers\, Roofers\, Sheet Me
 tal Workers\, and Tri-Council Temps.\, as is provided for by Minnesota Stat
 utes Section 13D.03</p><p dir="ltr">Following the closed session\, the Boar
 d shall continue in open session and\, if necessary\, shall discuss and tak
 e action with respect to labor negotiations.</p><br><p dir="ltr">July 13\, 
 2023</p><br><p dir="ltr">Jim Vue<br>Chair\, Board of Education</p><p dir="l
 tr">Independent School District No. 625 </p><p dir="ltr">Saint Paul Public 
 Schools</p>
