  property tax levy on<b> Tuesday\, December 3\, 2024 at 6:00 p.m. in Confer
 ence Rooms A and B of the Administration Building</b>\, located at 360 Colb
 orne Street.  The hearing shall include a brief presentation on the propose
 d levy\, followed by public comment.   <br>To provide a comment or ask a qu
 estion during the hearing\, please complete the <a href="https://www.spps.o
 rg/about/board-of-education/public-comment"><u>Form for Public Comment onli
 ne</u></a> or contact Board Secretary Sarah Dahlke at <a href="mailto:sarah
 .dahlke@spps.org"><u>sarah.dahlke@spps.org</u></a>. Please ensure comments 
