 tions after the meeting. If an interpreter is needed\, please call 651-767-
 8149 no later than Monday\, November 25\, 2024.    <br><br><br>Dated:  Nove
 mber 13\, 2024<br><br>Halla Henderson<br>Chair\, Board of Education<br>Inde
 pendent School District No. 625 <br>Saint Paul Public Schools
