 GS OF THE BOARD OF&nbsp\;</p><p>EDUCATION</p></b><br><b><u><br></u></b><br>
 </u><p>In the Matter of Board Action</p><p>Regarding Reopening Items</p><p>
 <br></p><p></p><p></p><br><b><p>To:&nbsp\;Directors of the Board of Educati
 on of Independent School&nbsp\;</p><p>District No. 625</p><br><p>PLEASE TAK
 E NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 12
