 e Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Pu
 blic Schools\, to be held and convened on:</p><br><ul><li><p>Monday\, April
  12\, 2021 commencing at 6:15 p.m.</p></li><li><p>Monday\, April 19\, 2021\
 ;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, April 26\, 2021\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, May 3\,
  2021\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, May 10\, 2021\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, May
  17\, 2021\;</p></li><li><p>and Monday\, May 24\, 2021.</p></li></ul><br><p
 >Each meeting will commence at 5:00 P.M\, unless otherwise noted\, via tele
 phonic and video conference during which the Board will consider and act on
  contract items regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021\, and any oth
 er matters regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021 and/or in response
  to COVID-19.</p><br><p>The public may monitor the open portions of the mee
 ting via live stream at&nbsp\;<a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps.or
 g/boe</a>.</p><br><p>April 2\, 2021</p><br><p>Jeanelle Foster<br>Chair\, Bo
 ard of Education</p><p>Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p>Saint 
