DESCRIPTION:<br>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625<br>SAINT PAUL PUBLIC SC
 HOOLS<br><br><u>NOTICE OF SPECIAL MEETING OF THE BOARD OF EDUCATION</u><br>
 <br>In the Matter of Truth in Taxation Hearing on Pay26 Levy<br><br><br>To:
  Directors of the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625
 <br><br><br>PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minneso
 ta Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, the Board of Education of Ind
 ependent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools shall hereby h
 old and convene a public hearing on the proposed 2026 property tax levy on<
 b> Tuesday\, December 2\, 2025 at 6:00 p.m. in Conference Rooms A and B of 
 the Administration Building</b>\, located at 360 Colborne Street.  The hear
 ing shall include a brief presentation on the proposed levy\, followed by p
 ublic comment.   <br>To provide a comment or ask a question during the hear
 ing\, please complete the<u><a target="_blank" href="https://www.spps.org/a
 bout/board-of-education/public-comment"> Form for Public Comment online</a>
 </u> or contact Board Secretary Sarah Dahlke at <u><a href="mailto:sarah.da
 hlke@spps.org">sarah.dahlke@spps.org</a></u>. Please ensure comments are th
 ree minutes or less. The district will follow up with individual questions 
