 f Education of Independent School&nbsp\;District No. 625</p><br><br><p>PLEA
 SE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Sect
 ion 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a special meeting of the Boa
 rd of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public 
 Schools\, to be held and convened on&nbsp\;Tuesday August 31\, 2021&nbsp\;i
 n Conference Rooms A and B of the Administration Building\, located at 360 
 Colborne Street.&nbsp\; The special meeting shall begin at 4:30 p.m.\, and 
 the Board and Administration will review and discuss a resolution regarding
  a COVID-19 vaccine requirement for all SPPS staff.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nb
 sp\;</p><br><p>Public comment will be scheduled for 4:30 p.m. to 5:30 p.m w
 ith the time allotment per speaker to be determined based on the number of 
