 of Education of Independent School District No. 625<br><br>PLEASE TAKE NOTI
 CE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\
 , Subdivision 6\, does hereby change the dates of the Committee of the Boar
 d meeting and Regular Meeting of the Board of Education for June 2025.<br><
 br>The <b>Committee of the Board meeting</b>\, originally scheduled for Tue
 sday\, June 10\, 2025 will now commence on <b>Tuesday\, June 17\, 2025</b>\
 , beginning at 4:30 p.m. at the District Administration Building located at
  360 Colborne Street in Conference Room 5A.<br><br>The <b>Regular Meeting o
 f the Board of Education</b>\, originally scheduled for Tuesday\, June 17\,
  2025\, will now commence on <b>Tuesday\, June 10\, 2025</b> beginning at 5
 :30 p.m. at the District Administration Building located at 360 Colborne St
 reet in Conference Rooms A and B.<br><br>May 22\, 2025<br><br>Halla Henders
 on <br>Chair\, Board of Education <br>Independent School District No. 625 S
 aint Paul Public Schools
