DESCRIPTION:The committee meets monthly (since January 2012) to review the 
 existing District 10 Land Use Plan of 2007 and the West Como Midway Parkway
  Small Area Plan of 1997\, as well as the recently adopted Lexington/Larpe​
 nteur Node Study\, and to compile a comprehensive up-to-date document that 
 will provide the City with our vision\, policy priorities and strategies we
  want to guide growth\, investment and development in our district. The com
 mittee is co-chaired by District 10 Land Use Committee member Chris Harknes
 s and a member of the City Planning Commission.\n \nIf you are an intereste
 d resident or business owner who would like to serve on this committee\, pl
 ease contact Jessie at the District 10 office at district10@dist​rict10como
 park.​org or 651-644-3889. 
