 &nbsp\;</p></b><b><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><span>To:</span><span>
 Directors of the Board of Education of Independent School&nbsp\;</span></p>
 <p><span>District No. 625</span></p><p><b><br><br></b></p><p><span>PLEASE T
 AKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 
 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby revise the agenda for the special mee
 ting of the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Sai
 nt Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on </span><span>Monday\, A
 pril 26\, 2021 beginning at 5:00 p.m. </span><span>in-person at District Ad
 ministration Building at 360 Colborne Street\, Saint Paul\, MN 55102\, as w
 ell as via telephonic and video conference during which the Board will hear
  public comment beginning at 5:00 p.m.\, and immediately following the adjo
 urnment of public comment or at 5:35 p.m.\, whichever comes first\, the Boa
 rd of Education will consider and act on items originally scheduled for the
  Regular Meeting of the Board of Education of April 20\, 2021.</span></p><p
 ><b><br></b></p><p><span>The public may monitor the open portions of the me
 eting via live stream at </span><a href="http://www.spps.org/boe"><span>www
