 </span></p><p><b></b><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p
 ><br></p><p>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</p><p>SAINT PAUL PUBLIC SCH
 OOLS</p><br>NOTICE OF SERIES OF SPECIAL</b><br><b><u><b><p>MEETINGS OF THE 
 BOARD OF&nbsp\;</p><p>EDUCATION</p></b><br><b><u><br></u></b><br></u><p>In 
 the Matter of Board Action</p><p>Regarding Reopening Items</p><p><br></p><p
 ></p><p></p><br><b><p>To:&nbsp\;Directors of the Board of Education of Inde
 pendent School&nbsp\;</p><p>District No. 625</p><br><p>PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\,
  that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Su
 bdivision 6\, does hereby call a series of special meetings of the Board of
  Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schoo
 ls\, to be held and convened on:</p><br><ul><li><p>Monday\, April 12\, 2021
  commencing at 6:15 p.m.</p></li><li><p>Monday\, April 19\, 2021\;</p></li>
 <li><p>Monday\, April 26\, 2021\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, May 3\, 2021\;</p
 ></li><li><p>Monday\, May 10\, 2021\;</p></li><li><p>Monday\, May 17\, 2021
 \;</p></li><li><p>and Monday\, May 24\, 2021.</p></li></ul><br><p>Each meet
 ing will commence at 5:00 P.M\, unless otherwise noted\, via telephonic and
  video conference during which the Board will consider and act on contract 
 items regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021\, and any other matters
  regarding reopening for school year 2020-2021 and/or in response to COVID-
 19.</p><br><p>The public may monitor the open portions of the meeting via l
 ive stream at&nbsp\;<a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps.org/boe</a>.
 </p><br><p>April 2\, 2021</p><br><p>Jeanelle Foster<br>Chair\, Board of Edu
 cation</p><p>Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p>Saint Paul Publi
 c Schools</b></b>
