 "ltr">SAINT PAUL PUBLIC SCHOOLS</p><br><u>NOTICE OF SPECIAL MEETING&nbsp\;<
 u>OF THE BOARD OF EDUCATION</u></u><br><br><p dir="ltr">In the Matter of Tr
 uth in Taxation Hearing&nbsp\;on Pay23 Levy<u></u></p><p dir="ltr"><u></u><
 /p><p dir="ltr"><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u>
 </u><u></u><u></u><u></u></p><br><br><p dir="ltr">To:&nbsp\;Directors of th
 e Board of Education of Independent School&nbsp\;District No. 625</p><p dir
 ="ltr"></p><br><br><p dir="ltr">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\,
  pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, the Board
  of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Sc
 hools shall hereby hold and convene a public hearing on the proposed 2023 p
 roperty tax levy on<b>&nbsp\;Tuesday\, December 6\, 2022 at 6:00 p.m. in Co
 nference Rooms A and B of the Administration Building</b>\, located at 360 
 Colborne Street.&nbsp\; The hearing shall include a brief presentation on t
 he proposed levy\, followed by public comment.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</p><p d
 ir="ltr">To provide a comment or ask a question during the hearing\, please
  complete the&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.spps.org/Page/31813"><u>Form for P
 ublic Comment online</u></a>&nbsp\;or contact Board Secretary Sarah Dahlke 
 at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:sarah.dahlke@spps.org"><u>sarah.dahlke@spps.org</u
 ></a>. Please ensure comments are three minutes or less. The district will 
 follow up with individual questions after the meeting. If an interpreter is
  needed\, please call 651-767-8334 no later than Tuesday\, November 22\, 20
 22.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</p><br><br><p dir="ltr">Dated:&nbsp\; Novem
 ber 15\, 2022</p><br><p dir="ltr">Jim Vue</p><p dir="ltr">Chair\, Board of 
 Education</p><p dir="ltr">Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p>Sai
 nt Paul Public Schools
