 oard of Education of Independent School&nbsp\;</p><p>District No. 625</p><b
 r><br><p>PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota 
 Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a special close
 d meeting of the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\
 , Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convened on&nbsp\;Tuesday\, Se
 ptember 15\, 2020 commencing at 4:00 p.m.&nbsp\;via telephonic and video co
 nference\, in which the Board shall move into a closed session to discuss t
 he annual performance evaluation of the Superintendent\, Joe Gothard\, as i
 s provided for by Minnesota Statutes Section 13D.05\, subd. 3(a).</p><br><p
 >The public may monitor the open portions of the meeting via live stream at
 &nbsp\;<a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps.org/boe</a>.</p><br><p>Se
 ptember 9\, 2020</p><p><br></p><p>Jeanelle Foster<br>Chair\, Board of Educa
 tion</p><p>Independent School District No. 625&nbsp\;</p>Saint Paul Public 
