DESCRIPTION:<br><b>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</b><p><b>SAINT PAUL 
 PUBLIC SCHOOLS</b></p><p><br></p><br><u>SPECIAL NOTICE FROM THE BOARD OF ED
 UCATION</u><br><p>In the Matter of a Series of Closed Meetings Regarding La
 bor Negotiations</p><p><u>_________________________________________________
 ___________________________</u></p><br><p>To: Directors of the Board of Edu
 cation of Independent School </p><p>District No. 625</p><br><br><p>PLEASE T
 AKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 
 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a series of special meetings of 
 the Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul 
 Public Schools\, to be held and convened on:</p><ul><li><p><b>Tuesday\, Jan
 uary 23\, 2024</b></p></li><li><p><b>Tuesday\, February 20\, 2024</b></p></
 li><li><p><b>Tuesday\, March 19\, 2024</b></p></li><li><p><b>Tuesday\, Apri
 l 23\, 2024</b></p></li></ul><br><p><b>Meetings will begin at 4:00 p.m. in 
 Conference Room 5A of the Administration Building located at 360 Colborne S
 treet</b>\, during which by majority public vote the Board shall move into 
 a closed session to consider strategy for labor negotiations\, including ne
 gotiation strategies\, developments\, discussion\, and review of labor nego
 tiation proposals for these bargaining units including ASAP\, Educational A
 ssistants\, Principals\, School and Community Service Professionals\, Teach
 ers\, MMSA\, PEA\, AFSCME\, Bus Drivers\, CCEA\, Custodians\, Tri-Council\,
  Electricians\, Glaziers\, Pipe fitters\, Plumbers\, Sheet Metal Workers\, 
 and Tri-Council Temps.\, as is provided for by Minnesota Statutes Section 1
 3D.03</p><br><p>Following the closed session\, the Board shall continue in 
 open session and\, if necessary\, shall discuss and take action with respec
 t to labor negotiations.</p><br><p>January 18\, 2024</p><p><br></p><p>Halla
  Henderson<br>Chair\, Board of Education</p><p>Independent School District 
 No. 625 </p><p>Saint Paul Public Schools</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240130T203222Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special (Closed) Meeting re: Labor Negotiations
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
