  PUBLIC SCHOOLS</b><br><u>SPECIAL NOTICE FROM THE BOARD OF EDUCATION</u><br
 ><br>In the Matter of a Special Meeting Regarding Search Firm Selection for
  the Superintendent Search<br><u>__________________________________________
 __________________________________</u><br><br>To: Directors of the Board of
  Education of Independent School <br>District No. 625<br><br><br>        PL
 EASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Se
 ction 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a special meeting of the B
 oard of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Publi
 c Schools\, to be held and convened on<b> Tuesday\, July 9\, 2024 beginning
  at 4:00 p.m. in Conference Room 5A of the District Administration Building
  located at 360 Colborne</b>.  This meeting will be audio recorded.<br>Duri
 ng the meeting\, the Board shall receive information and presentations from
  selected search firms. The Board will listen to presentations from search 
 firms\, interview each firm\, then discuss and select a preferred firm to u
 tilize for the Superintendent Search. The Board will vote on a resolution a
 pproving a preferred search firm and authorizing contract negotiations.<br>
 <br>June 26\, 2024<br><br>Halla Henderson<br>Chair\, Board of Education<br>
 Independent School District No. 625 <br>Saint Paul Public Schools
