CREATED:20201026T143520Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Saint Paul Public Schools public hearing on the proposed 202
 1 property tax levy is&nbsp\;<strong>Tuesday\, December 8\, 2020\, at 6 p.m
 .</strong>\, and will be conducted virtually. The hearing will include a br
 ief presentation on the proposed levy\, followed by public comment.&nbsp\; 
 &nbsp\;</p><p>If an interpreter is needed\, please call 651-767-8334 no lat
 er than Monday\, November 23\, 2020.</p><p>The hearing will be streamed liv
 e online and will air on Saint Paul Cable Channel 16. To provide a comment 
 or ask a question during the hearing\, please contact Board Secretary Sarah
  Dahlke at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:sarah.dalke@spps.org">sarah.dahlke@spps.or
 g</a>&nbsp\;and request to join the hearing remotely through your computer 
 or phone. Please ensure comments are three minutes or less. The district wi
 ll follow up with individual questions after the meeting.&nbsp\;</p><p><str
 ong>Note:</strong>&nbsp\;requests to join the meeting live must be received
 &nbsp\;<strong>by Monday\, December 7</strong>\, before 5 p.m.&nbsp\;&nbsp\
