DESCRIPTION:<b><br><p>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625</p><p>SAINT PAUL 
 PUBLIC SCHOOLS</p><br><b><br></b></b>NOTICE OF SPECIAL MEETING<b><br></b>OF
  THE BOARD OF EDUCATION<br><p style="">In the Matter of Interviews for Boar
 d Vacancy</p><p style="font-weight: bold\;"></p><p style="font-weight: bold
 \;"></p><br><br><p style="font-weight: bold\;">To:Directors of the Board of
  Education of Independent School&nbsp\;</p><p style="font-weight: bold\;">D
 istrict No. 625</p><br><br><p style="">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the unders
 igned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, do
 es hereby call a special meeting of the Board of Education of Independent S
 chool District No. 625\, Saint Paul Public Schools\, to be held and convene
 d on Monday\, July 27\, 2020\, commencing at 4:00 P.M. via telephonic and v
 ideo conference to conduct interviews of selected applicants for the board 
 vacancy\, after which the Board of Education will make its selection of the
  applicant to fill the position vacated by Marny Xiong on June 7\, 2020.&nb
 sp\; The Board may then act on a Resolution Filling School Board Vacancy by
  Appointment.</p><br><p style="">The public may monitor the open portions o
 f the meeting via live stream at <a href="http://www.spps.org/boe">www.spps
 .org/boe</a>.</p><br><p style="">July 2\, 2020</p><p style="">Jeanelle Fost
 er<br>Vice Chair\, Board of Education</p><p style="">Independent School Dis
 trict No. 625&nbsp\;</p><p style="">Saint Paul Public Schools</p>
