CREATED:20241212T164047Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>INDEPENDENT SCHOOL DISTRICT NO. 625<br>SAINT PAUL PUBLIC SC
 HOOLS<br><br><u><br></u><br><u>SPECIAL NOTICE FROM THE BOARD OF EDUCATION</
 u><br><u><br></u><br>In the Matter of A Series of Special Meetings Regardin
 g Superintendent Search <br><br><u>________________________________________
 ____________________________________</u><br><br>To: Directors of the Board 
 of Education of Independent School District No. 625<br><br><br>PLEASE TAKE 
 NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minnesota Statutes Section 123B
 .09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby call a series of special meetings of the 
 Board of Education of Independent School District No. 625\, Saint Paul Publ
 ic Schools\, to be held and convened on:<br><ul><li><b><br>Monday\, Decembe
 r 16\, 2024</b></li><li><b><br>Tuesday\, December 17\, 2024</b></li><li><b>
 <br>Wednesday\, December 18\, 2024</b></li></ul><br><br><b>Meetings will co
 mmence at 6:00 p.m. in Conference Rooms A and B of the Administration Build
 ing located at 360 Colborne Street</b>\, during which the Board will conduc
 t public interviews of the finalists for the position of Superintendent of 
 Saint Paul Public Schools.  <br><br>The schedule of finalist interviews is:
 <ul><li><b><br>Monday\, December 16\, 2024</b><ul><li><br>Dr. Rhoda Mhiripi
 ri-Reed</li></ul></li><li><br><b>Tuesday\, December 17\, 2024</b><ul><li><b
 r>Dr. Brenda Cassellius</li></ul></li><li><b><br>Wednesday\, December 18\, 
 2024</b><ul><li><br>Dr. Stacie Stanley</li></ul></li></ul><br><br>They will
  be televised and livestreamed at <u><a target="_blank" href="https://spps.
 eduvision.tv/LiveSched.aspx/">https://spps.eduvision.tv/LiveSched.aspx/</a>
 </u>.<br><br>Following the interview on December 18\, 2024\, the Board may 
 act on the selection of the new superintendent or instead may act on the se
 lection at the December 19\, 2024 special regular meeting.<br><br>December 
 12\, 2024<br><br>Halla Henderson<br>Chair\, Board of Education<br>Independe
 nt School District No. 625 <br>Saint Paul Public Schools
LAST-MODIFIED:20241212T164325Z
LOCATION:360 Colborne Street
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special Meeting on Superintendent Search
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
