 ><p dir="ltr">PLEASE TAKE NOTICE\, that the undersigned\, pursuant to Minne
 sota Statutes Section 123B.09\, Subdivision 6\, does hereby notice that a p
 otential of a quorum of directors may be present at an upcoming community e
 vent\, <b>Safer SPPS: Community Conversation &amp\; Dinner on Thursday\, Ma
 rch 30\, 2023 from 6-9 p.m. at Washington Technology Magnet School (1495 Ri
 ce Street).  </b>No official board business will be conducted.  SPPS studen
 ts and families\, staff and community members are invited to share a meal a
 nd discuss ways to improve safety in our school communities.</p><br><p dir=
